              <div class="inner-container px-3 px-md-4 py-3">
                <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            
    <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The returns on venture capital will vary between different investment opportunities. It will depend on the growth and profitability of the business you invest in and how long the investment is made for. The return in the investment is made on ‘exit’ or ‘liquidity event’. This is usually when the property development or business is sold, or through an initial public offering (IPO) on the stock market. The returns from successful early-stage investments can be very high, but these investment opportunities also come with a high risk.</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

        </div>
                  
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

            
            
