How to find the right venture capital to fund your business in Sydney? </h3>
                  <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                      
                      <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
                          <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            
    <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One way to fund your business in Sydney is to launch a </span><a href="https://www.venturecrowd.com.au/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">crowdfunding</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> campaign. VentureCrowd, an investor-led, co-investment platform, allows you to raise and secure capital through equity-based crowdfunding from a large and fast-growing crowd of investors in collaboration with our experienced team. Whether you’re an entrepreneur, a property developer, or an established business owner we give you access to alternative finance from a crowd of both retail and sophisticated investors. And you’ll have the opportunity to connect with investors or individuals who are familiar with the sector or market your business so you’ll be able to draw on their experience.&nbsp;</span></p>

        </div>
    </div>
<div class="divider-wrap" data-alignment="default"><div style="height: 10px;" class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you need extra support, we also have a range of campaign services including digital marketing and PR to help you promote your campaign, and you’ll also have a dedicated campaign manager. Usually, a funding round runs for six weeks, and with VentureCrowd, the average investment is $35K per investor. Although there is no maximum or minimum amount of money you can raise through VentureCrowd, you’ll need to disclose the total amount of the current raise and allocate a set amount to VentureCrowd investors.</span></p>

        </div>
    </div>
<div class="divider-wrap" data-alignment="default"><div style="height: 10px;" class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;If you are thinking about the best way to raise and secure capital for your startup or property development, speak to the team at VentureCrowd. We have the experience and knowledge to help you, as well as a proven track record so you know you’ll be in safe hands. If you have any questions about venture capital in Sydney or would like more information about VentureCrowd, our team love to hear from you. Give us a call on <a href="tel:1300039655">1300 039 655</a> or email <a href="mailto:hello@venturecrowd.com.au">hello@venturecrowd.com.au&nbsp;</a></span></p>

